      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software must be under full configuration management with documented V&V testing, traceable issue tracking, and independent code review consistent with MRL 5 requirements.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver is a commercially validated package with documented release testing and version control. Standard engineering QA practices are followed and the development team has extensive experience with hemolysis modeling workflows. Minor gaps in independent review coverage are considered acceptable given the maturity of the solver platform."
