      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy verification using manufactured solutions or benchmark problems must demonstrate expected convergence rates for all governing equations employed.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy tests using the method of manufactured solutions confirm second-order spatial convergence for momentum and scalar transport equations. Results are consistent with published FDA pump benchmark studies."
