      "rationale": "Quantitative validation metrics were computed for hemolysis index and pressure-flow curves at all operating points. Experimental uncertainty was characterized through repeat measurements. Simulation numerical uncertainty was propagated via Monte Carlo sampling of inlet boundary conditions."
