      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on its established performance for rotating machinery flows. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model was applied consistently with published FDA pump studies. Model form uncertainty was estimated through comparison with an alternative Lagrangian damage accumulation approach."
    },
